hurdcog-occ-bridge (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of HurdCog-OCC integration bridge
  * Implements AtomSpace-HurdCog bidirectional communication
  * Provides MachSpace synchronization with OpenCog AtomSpace
  * Integrates Cognumach microkernel with cognitive primitives
  * Enables three-layer cognitive synergy architecture
  * Supports attention-driven resource allocation across layers
  * Facilitates cross-layer reasoning and learning loops
  * Provides unified integration framework for AGI-OS

